diagrams.mermaid:
flowchart TD
  Start([新診斷 Ovarian Mass]) --> Biopsy{病理確認}

  Biopsy -->|Borderline LMP<br>非侵入性| LMP[**Borderline path**:<br>**化療無益處 — 純手術切除**<br>Comprehensive staging + Observe<br>**NACT 不適用**]
  Biopsy -->|SCCOHT 高血鈣型| SCCOHT_path[**SCCOHT path（LCOC-5 新章節）**:<br>Germline SMARCA4 testing 必考<br>三聯徵: 年輕 + 高血鈣 + 卵巢腫塊<br>→ 前往 3️⃣ 樹 SCCOHT 分支]
  Biopsy -->|Invasive Epithelial OC| Imaging[CT abdomen/pelvis<br>CA125 / HE4<br>biopsy or paracentesis cytology]

  Imaging --> Stage{Stage 評估}

  Stage -->|Stage I 局限| Surg_I[Primary staging surgery<br>TAH+BSO+omentectomy<br>+ washing + LN sampling]

  Stage -->|Stage II-IV| Resectable{可達 R0?<br>PS / 瘤量 / CT 預測}

  Resectable -->|是| PDS[**Primary Debulking Surgery PDS**<br>目標 R0<br>+ retroperitoneal LND]

  Resectable -->|否| NACT[**Neoadjuvant Chemo × 3 cycles**<br>Carbo AUC 5-6 + Pac 175 mg/m²<br>Q3W<br>⚠️ 不適用 Borderline / 非侵入性]

  NACT --> IDS[**Interval Debulking Surgery IDS**<br>**HIPEC 可加（主流程）**<br>Cisplatin 100 mg/m² 42°C × 90 分鐘<br>OVHIPEC-1 OS HR 0.67]

  IDS --> Chemo3[再 chemo × 3 cycles]

  Surg_I --> Histology{Histology + Risk}
  Histology -->|IA G1 Endometrioid<br>IA LGSC<br>IA Mucinous Expansile| FertOption{Fertility-sparing 候選?<br>**僅 low-risk histology + 單側**}
  Histology -->|IC 任何 / IB high-grade /<br>IC Clear Cell / Mucinous Infiltrative| Adj_Chemo[Adjuvant Pac/Carbo × 6 cycles Q3W]
  Histology -->|IA Clear Cell / IA high-grade serous| Adj_Option[化療 × 6 或 observation 個案化<br>**Clear cell + High-grade 不建議 fertility-sparing**<br>除非 IA + 充分告知風險]

  FertOption -->|是 + 強烈希望| FS[**Fertility-sparing**:<br>單側 USO + comprehensive staging<br>限 Grade 1 Endometrioid / LGSC /<br>Mucinous Expansile 等 low-risk histology]
  FertOption -->|否| Adj_Option

  PDS --> Adj_Chemo
  Chemo3 --> Mol_Test[**Germline + somatic<br>biomarker testing**<br>BRCA1/2 P/LP variants<br>+ HRD + tumor markers]
  Adj_Chemo --> Mol_Test

  Mol_Test --> Maint([前往 2️⃣ Maintenance 樹])

  classDef lmp fill:#e8e8f0,stroke:#5a5a8a;
  class LMP lmp;
  classDef sccoht fill:#ffe0d0,stroke:#a83a3a;
  class SCCOHT_path sccoht;
  classDef early fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class Surg_I,FS early;
  classDef mid fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class PDS,NACT,IDS mid;
  classDef sys fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class Adj_Chemo,Chemo3 sys;

flowchart TD
  Start([完成 1L Pac/Carbo × 6<br>CR / PR]) --> BevUsed{1L 是否有用 Bev?}

  BevUsed -->|有用 Bev| BevYes{BRCA / HRD status?}
  BevUsed -->|未用 Bev| BevNo{BRCA / HRD status?}

  BevNo -->|BRCA1/2 P/LP variant| BNo_BRCA[**首選 Cat 1**:<br>Olaparib 單藥 (SOLO-1)<br>OR Niraparib (PRIMA)<br>OR Rucaparib]

  BevNo -->|HRD+ non-BRCA| BNo_HRD[**首選**:<br>Niraparib (PRIMA HRD+ HR 0.43)<br>OR Rucaparib<br>**⭐ Olaparib 單藥 Cat 2B（v.3.2025 新增）**]

  BevNo -->|HRP / Unknown| BNo_HRP[**首選**:<br>Niraparib (PRIMA HRP HR 0.68)<br>OR Rucaparib<br>**不選 Olaparib 單藥**]

  BevYes -->|BRCA1/2 P/LP variant| BYes_BRCA[**首選 Cat 1**:<br>Olaparib + Bevacizumab (PAOLA-1)<br>continue Bev to 22 cycles total]

  BevYes -->|HRD+ non-BRCA| BYes_HRD[**首選 Cat 1**:<br>Olaparib + Bevacizumab (PAOLA-1)<br>HRD+ subgroup PFS 28.1 vs 16.6 月]

  BevYes -->|HRP / Unknown| BYes_HRP[**首選**:<br>Niraparib (或 Rucaparib)<br>OR Bevacizumab maintenance only<br>**PAOLA-1 在 HRD- 無顯著益處**]

  BNo_BRCA --> FollowUp[追蹤<br>CA125 + CT Q3M × 2yr<br>之後 Q6M]
  BNo_HRD --> FollowUp
  BNo_HRP --> FollowUp
  BYes_BRCA --> FollowUp
  BYes_HRD --> FollowUp
  BYes_HRP --> FollowUp

  classDef brca fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class BNo_BRCA,BYes_BRCA brca;
  classDef hrd fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class BNo_HRD,BYes_HRD hrd;
  classDef hrp fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class BNo_HRP,BYes_HRP hrp;

flowchart TD
  Start([Recurrent ovarian cancer]) --> Histology{Histology?}

  Histology -->|SCCOHT| SCCOHT_branch[**🆕 SCCOHT path (LCOC-5)**:<br>VPCBAE / PAVEP / BEP<br>+ **Auto-SCT consolidation**<br>轉介幹細胞中心]
  Histology -->|LGSC / G1 Endometrioid| LGSC_path[**LGSC path**：詳見下方]
  Histology -->|Mucinous| Muc_path[**Mucinous path**：詳見下方]
  Histology -->|HGSC / G2-3 Endo /<br>Carcinosarcoma / Clear cell| PFI_check{Platinum-Free Interval}

  PFI_check -->|>6 月| PS_path[**Platinum-Sensitive**<br>重新挑戰 platinum]
  PFI_check -->|≤6 月| PR_path[**Platinum-Resistant**]

  PS_path --> PS_choice{Regimen 選擇}
  PS_choice --> PS_PldCarbo[Carboplatin + PLD CALYPSO]
  PS_choice --> PS_GemCarbo[Carbo + Gemcitabine ± Bev OCEANS / GOG-213]
  PS_choice --> PS_CarboPac[Carbo + Paclitaxel ± Bev AGO-OVAR-2.5]

  PS_PldCarbo --> PS_Response{Response<br>CR / PR?}
  PS_GemCarbo --> PS_Response
  PS_CarboPac --> PS_Response

  PS_Response -->|Yes + BRCA P/LP| SOLO2[**SOLO-2 maintenance**<br>Olaparib 維持治療<br>⚠️ **PARPi 單藥 active treatment 已撤銷**<br>PFS 19.1 vs 5.5 月]
  PS_Response -->|Yes + HRD+| ARIEL3[**ARIEL3 / NOVA maintenance**<br>Rucaparib 或 Niraparib 維持<br>⚠️ **僅作 maintenance，非 monotherapy**]
  PS_Response -->|No response| PR_path

  PR_path --> PR_first{**Preferred 首選**}
  PR_first --> NabPac_Rel[**🆕 nab-Paclitaxel + Relacorilant**<br>v.4.2026 新首選<br>適用 ≤3 線 + 曾用 Bev<br>**⚠️ 禁用 steroid premedication**]
  PR_first --> HER2_test{HER2 IHC}
  PR_first --> FRa_test{FRα IHC<br>VENTANA assay}

  HER2_test -->|IHC 3+ 或 2+| TDXd[**Fam-trastuzumab deruxtecan-nxki<br>(Enhertu, T-DXd)**<br>5.4 mg/kg IV Q3W]

  FRa_test -->|FRα ≥75% High| MIRASOL_mono[**Mirvetuximab 單藥**<br>MIRASOL OS 16.5 vs 12.8 月 HR 0.67]
  FRa_test -->|FRα ≥50% 或 ≥25%| MIRASOL_combo[**Mirvetuximab + Bevacizumab Cat 2B**]

  PR_path --> PR_chemo[單藥化療:<br>PLD 40-50 mg/m² Q4W<br>Topotecan 4 mg/m² weekly<br>Weekly paclitaxel 80 mg/m²<br>Gemcitabine ± Bev AURELIA]

  PR_chemo --> Salvage[後線 salvage:<br>Trabectedin + PLD<br>Etoposide PO<br>**MSI-H/dMMR or TMB-H: Pembrolizumab IV 或 SC**<br>Clinical trial]
  NabPac_Rel --> Salvage
  TDXd --> Salvage
  MIRASOL_mono --> Salvage
  MIRASOL_combo --> Salvage

  LGSC_path --> LGSC_branch{KRAS mut?}
  LGSC_branch -->|KRAS mut| Avu[**Avutometinib + Defactinib**<br>v.3.2025 新核准<br>KRAS-mut recurrent LGSC]
  LGSC_branch -->|KRAS wt 或 unknown| LGSC_other[**MEK inhibitor**：<br>Trametinib / Binimetinib<br>OR Hormone：Letrozole / Anastrozole<br>OR Carbo + Pac]

  Muc_path --> Muc_choice{Choice}
  Muc_choice -->|採大腸直腸路徑| FOLFIRI[**FOLFIRI ± Bevacizumab Cat 2B**]
  Muc_choice -->|standard| Muc_std[Carbo + Pac<br>或 PLD / weekly Pac]

